@idempotencyKey = smoke-check-key-001

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Auth health
GET {{apiUrl}}/auth/health

### Booking health
GET {{apiUrl}}/booking/health

### Integrations health
GET {{apiUrl}}/integrations/health

### Login start
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}"
}

### Login verify
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "loginSessionId": "{{loginSessionId}}",
  "otpCode": "{{otpCode}}"
}

### Me
GET {{apiUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Orders list
GET {{apiUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Order card
GET {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Order documents
GET {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Resend documents
POST {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/documents/resend
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Order events
GET {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Exchange quote
POST {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/exchange/quote
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Exchange confirm
POST {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/exchange/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quoteId": "{{exchangeOperationId}}"
}

### Exchange operation
GET {{apiUrl}}/exchange-operations/{{exchangeOperationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refund quote
POST {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/refund/quote
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refund confirm
POST {{apiUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/refund/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}-refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quoteId": "{{refundOperationId}}"
}

### Refund operation
GET {{apiUrl}}/refund-operations/{{refundOperationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Booking lookup by PNR + surname
POST {{apiUrl}}/booking/lookup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pnr": "B2FLEX",
  "passengerLastName": "IVANOV"
}

### Booking lookup by ticket + surname
POST {{apiUrl}}/booking/lookup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticketNumber": "421000000102",
  "passengerLastName": "PETROVA"
}

### Suggested order mapping from seed
# B2FLEX  -> flexible exchange, refund available
# B2PAY1  -> exchange with surcharge
# B2NREF  -> refund blocked
# B2CANC  -> cancelled order
# B2FAIL  -> commit failure scenario
